text: Lai Chu-long (born 10 March 1942) is a Taiwanese gymnast. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Taiwan Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
